<!-- RLVisionKick 带球丢球测试: 不走射门决策和 Adjust, 近球后直接进入视觉带球; 丢球后继续向前走 -->

<root BTCPP_format="4">
    <include path="./subtrees/subtree_cam_find_and_track_ball.xml" />
    <include path="./subtrees/subtree_auto_standup_and_locate.xml" />

    <BehaviorTree ID="MainTree">
        <Sequence name="root">
            <RunOnce>
                <Script code="control_state=3; had_ball=false" />
            </RunOnce>
            <ReactiveSequence name="RLVisionKick 不射门带球测试">
                <Speak text="test" />
                <SubTree ID="AutoGetUpAndLocate" _autoremap="true" />
                <SubTree ID="CamFindAndTrackBall" _autoremap="true" />
                <Sequence _while="ball_location_known">
                    <Script code="had_ball=true" />
                    <SimpleChase _while="ball_range>=1.4" vx_limit="0.7" vy_limit="0.25" stop_dist="1.0" stop_angle="0.3" />
                    <RLVisionKick _while="ball_range&lt;1.4" min_msec_kick="1500" max_msec_kick="7000" range="6.0" />
                </Sequence>
                <Sequence _while="!ball_location_known &amp;&amp; had_ball">
                    <SetVelocity x="0.28" y="0.0" theta="0.0" />
                </Sequence>
                <Sequence _while="!ball_location_known &amp;&amp; !had_ball">
                    <SetVelocity />
                </Sequence>
            </ReactiveSequence>
        </Sequence>
    </BehaviorTree>
</root>
